<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2>
	Introduction</h2>
<p><img alt="eBook image" src="files/eBook&#32;image_7.jpg" style="margin: 8px 16px 8px 0px; float: left;" />This is a listing of 157 sites that legally offer free romance ebooks, for reading.</p>
<p>There is a separate listing of free audiobooks in the genre at </p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong><a href="free-audiobooks-romance" target="_blank">Free Romance Audiobooks Online</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>All of these sites listed have content that is legal for them to distribute and for you to read and or download.  If you find that any site listed is offering content that can not be legally transferred, please let me know in the comments below. </p>
<p>This list is not comprehensive and if you know of any other sites please post in the comments below or at our <a href="freeware-forum/index.html" target="_blank">forums</a>. </p>
<p>A comprehensive alphabetical listing of free books for reading or listening can be found on these pages:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<a href="best-free-ebooks-online.htm" target="_blank"><strong>Best Free eBooks Online</strong></a>  (913 sites)</li>
	<li>
		<a href="free-books-audio" target="_blank"><strong>Best Free Audio Books Online</strong></a>  (224 sites)</li>
</ul>
<p>For a complete listing of the free ebook pages here at Gizmo's, see</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong><a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/free-ebooks-audio-books" target="_blank">Free eBooks and Audio Books To Read Online or Download</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p>There will be other romance novels at sites listed there, but they are not categorized at the sites.</p>
<p>Libraries are also an excellent source for reading and listening materials.  To find out more information on your local library, the links here may help:  <a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/content/50-places-free-books-online.htm#libraries" target="_blank"><strong>Library Information</strong></a></p>
<p>Also, if you just came here looking for free ebooks, I would suggest that you take a look at the rest of the site.  The free ebooks listings are a small part of the great information available here.  This site is mainly for review of free softwares.  Each of the reviewers is a volunteer and has a personal interest in their software category, so you will get an unbiased review from an enthusiast of that software type.  In almost all cases, a free software can do the task of any paid software just as well, if not better.</p>
<h2>
	Free Romance eBooks</h2>
<p><a href="http://2020ok.com/23.htm" target="_blank"><strong>2020k </strong></a>has a good size collection of links divided into sub-categories such as historical, fantasy/ghost etc.  This site has a habit of throwing some unrelated works into the subcategories, but most of these appear OK.  <strong>Note:</strong>  Most of the links here are working, but there are a number that lead to BookRags, which are not free anymore.  Unfortunately, there is no way of telling where the link goes until you click the link.  Since they did fix the issue with archive.org links, hopefully they will fix this. Thanks to Marie99 for pointing this out.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://changelingpress.com/ezine/encounters.php" target="_blank">A Cheeky Changeling</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />offers over 100 free short stories either for free reading online or free download without registration.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.adamdecker.com/The%20Janitor.htm" target="_blank"><strong>AdamDecker</strong></a> offers his novel, The Janitor, for free reading online.  He also offers some free short stories and poems.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.allromanceebooks.com/category180.html" target="_blank"><strong>AllRomanceBooks</strong></a>  offers 278 free romance ebooks.  Registration is required.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/bestsellers/digital-text/158566011/" target="_blank"><strong>Amazon</strong></a>  has 50 free romance novels for download in kindle format.  To see all available free Romance novels at Amazon the hints provided in my article, <strong><a href="http://www.techsupportalert.com/free-books-kindle" target="_blank">Free Kindle eBooks Online (Legally)</a></strong>, should be used as there is definitely more than the 50 free ebooks linked here.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.amirapress.com/index.php?main_page=index&amp;cPath=34&amp;zenid=cee2q41hpt2frin78k67ug6au4" target="_blank">Amira Press  </a></strong>offers 6 free romance novels, available for free download in PDF without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.endofagedeception.com/" target="_blank">Angela Kay</a></strong>  offers her novel, <em>End of the Age:  Final Deception,</em> for free download in PDF.  A Christian novel about faith, courage and love involving fallen angels who return to Earth disguised as aliens.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://authormarketingclub.com/members/free-kindle-books/" target="_blank">Author Marketing Club</a></strong>   monitors Amazon (USA) for daily free ebook offerings. The amount listed varies from day to day.  They do offer genre selection and every daily listing that I saw had free Romance books.  You do have to go into each daily listing individually and then you are able to click on the Romance genre link for that listing.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://shop.authorstand.com/search.aspx?searchTerms=&amp;searchGenre=13&amp;searchAuthor=" target="_blank">Author Stand  </a></strong>has several hundred free romance works, many are short stories.  These are unique works by unpublished authors.  Registration is required for free PDF download.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://bargainebookhunter.com/tag/fiction-romance/" target="_blank">Bargain eBook Hunter</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings in the Romance category.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.barnesandnoble.com/s?view=grid&amp;PRC=0&amp;store=EBOOK&amp;startat=1&amp;sort=d&amp;size=20&amp;dref=2565" target="_blank">Barnes&amp;Noble</a></strong> has 205 free romance novels available for download.  Requires free registration and also requires credit card information.  Tried downloads through their PC software and could not connect online.  The books I checked on all were available elsewhere and better to get from those sources.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bestebooksfree.com/" target="_blank">Best eBooks Free </a></strong> <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />a mix of bargain and limited time free ebook offerings from Amazon (USA) separated into several genres.  eMail updates by genre are available.  This link is to the  main page where you can access Historical Romance, Contemporary Romance or Paranormal Romance Categories.   Thanks to <em>Rayven </em>for this site.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bestebooksworld.com/cat/Romance/" target="_blank"><strong>BesteBooksWorld</strong></a> has about 60 novels in its romance category and sub-categories for adult and young adult.  Since they link to other sites, the download and viewing options vary.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://bibliofaction.com/read/Search.aspx?category=Romantic" target="_blank">BiblioFaction</a></strong>  has over 750 free romantic short stories available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bibliotastic.com/genres/romance" target="_blank">Bibliotastic</a></strong> has 23 free original romance novels available for free reading online if not registered there.  All books there are free and so is registration.  Registration will open options to download in PDF, EPUB and PRC (Kindle).</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookiejar.com/home/browse?cat=19660800&amp;price=3&amp;status=2&amp;c=release&amp;type=Books" target="_blank">Bookie Jar </a></strong>has over 300 free ebooks in its Romance Classics category.  All are available for free reading online without registration. Free registration is required for free download in EPUB or MOBI (Kindle).  There are also 7 free ebooks in its <strong><a href="http://www.bookiejar.com/home/browse?cat=19660800&amp;price=0&amp;status=2&amp;c=release&amp;type=Books" target="_blank">Romance-Indie</a></strong> category.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookrix.com/library.html?page=1&amp;filterby=1&amp;sortby=date&amp;show=overview&amp;charts=&amp;category=56&amp;submitted1=&amp;searchlang=en&amp;searchdivsize=&amp;user=&amp;search=#b" target="_blank">BookRix </a></strong>has almost 2,000 free unique romance novels.  These are available for free reading online and free download in EPUB.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.booksie.com/romance" target="_blank">Booksie</a></strong>  a large collection of original works by generally unpublished authors available for free reading online.  Content includes short stories, poetry and novels.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.booksinmyphone.com/?tag=romance" target="_blank"><strong>Books In My Phone </strong></a>offers 49 public domain romance novels for free download in several formats compatible with all Java compatible phones.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.booksshouldbefree.com/genre/Romance" target="_blank"><strong>BooksShouldBeFree</strong></a> has a large collection of classic romance audio books for download in MP3 (zipped) and also has links to text versions of the books.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookstrand.com/free-reads" target="_blank">Book Strand</a></strong>   offers 348 free romance novels in varying ebook formats.  All appear to be available for free reading online, free EPUB download and some free Kindle compatible download, as well as some other formats.  Free registration is required to complete the checkout.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bookyards.com/categories.html?type=books&amp;category_id=117" target="_blank"><u><strong>BookYards (Romance)</strong></u></a> 162 novels available for download in pdf</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.breathlesspress.com/index.php?main_page=index&amp;cPath=19&amp;zenid=bs3kuuut8disomj5f6diirdje4" target="_blank">Breathless Press</a></strong>   offers 13 free romance novels for download in several ebook formats.  All are available in PDF, EPUB and Kindle compatible MOBI, as well as 4 other ebook formats.  Free registration is required.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bregdanchronicles.com/" target="_blank">Bregdan Chronicles</a></strong> Ginny Dye, offers the first book in The Bregdan Chronicles series for free download in PDF or for free reading online.  Submission of a valid email is necessary.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.talewins.com/Browzer/novels.htm" target="_blank">BrowzerBooks</a> </strong>now hosted on Talewins, offers some classic works for reading online or download in pdf  or in exe format (simulates book pages turning).  They also offer some unique works that they have commissioned to be updated.  Free registration is not required, but will notify you of their latest listings and allow you to forward the books on to others (with a "from me" page added). </p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.buzzle.com/chapters/escape-hatch_short-fixion_love-and-romance.asp" target="_blank">Buzzle</a></strong> is a site for unpublished authors and has a large selection of unique works.  This is a mix of short stories and novels.  Unfortunately the novels are released a chapter at a time and the system is not set up well as to viewing all available chapters.  These are all available for free reading online.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://drmfree.calibre-ebook.com/by/genre/romance?by=price" target="_blank">Calibre Open Books</a></strong> has 12 free ebooks in its Romance genre listing.  Download and viewing options vary as these are links offsite.  These are recent works, not classics.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://centslessbooks.com/romance.html" target="_blank">Centsless Books</a></strong> monitors Amazon (USA) for the top 100 free ebooks in the Romance genre.  Updated hourly.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.chrisslusser.com/novels/index.html" target="_blank"><strong>Chris Lusser</strong></a>  offers three of her romance novels for free download in several formats.</p>
<p><a href="http://romance-books.classic-literature.co.uk/" target="_blank"><strong>ClassicLiteratureLibrary</strong></a>  offers the public domain works of Jane Austen and the Memoirs of Jacques Casanova for online viewing.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.classicly.com/romance" target="_blank"><strong>Classicly</strong></a> has a nice collection of free classic romance novels available for download in PDF or for Kindle as well as online reading.  Links to many of the books are in the introduction paragraphs at the top of the page.  Thanks to Tyler G for this suggestion.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.dailyfreebooks.co.uk/free_ebooks/latest/?catID=49&amp;source=both" target="_blank">Daily Free Books (UK)</a></strong>  monitors Amazon (UK) for its daily free offerings.  They offer genre selection as well as sorting by time (including since your last visit).  They also offer free listings from Smashwords, which can be viewed with the Amazon offerings, alone or not at all (Amazon only).  This link is to the Romance genre with listings from both Amazon and Smashwords.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.dailyfreebooks.com/free_ebooks/latest/?source=both&amp;catID=49" target="_blank">Daily Free Books (USA)</a></strong>  monitors Amazon (USA) for its daily free offerings.  They offer genre selection as well as sorting by time (including since your last visit).  Like the sister UK site above, they offer free listings from Smashwords, which can be viewed with the Amazon offerings, alone or not at all (Amazon only).  This link is to the Romance genre with listings from both Amazon and Smashwords.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.dailylit.com/tags/romance/date/1" target="_blank"><strong>DailyLit</strong></a> has 14 classic romance novels available in installments that are mailed to your email or by RSS feed.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.diesel-ebooks.com/category/FRE027001/Romance/Free-Romance/1.html" target="_blank">Diesel eBooks</a></strong> has 640 free ebooks in its romance category available for free download in EPUB.  Registration is required.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.digilibraries.com/category/620/Fiction-Romance/" target="_blank">DigiLibraries</a></strong> has 454 free novels in its Romance category.  All are available for free reading online or download in EPUB or MOBI.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.digitalbookindex.org/_SEARCH/search010fictromana.asp" target="_blank">Digital Book Index</a></strong> has links to several hundred free romance works.  These are links offsite, so download and viewing options vary, but they do list the format in the link.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.eastoftheweb.com/short-stories/romanceindex.html" target="_blank">East of the Web </a></strong>has a good size collection of romance short stories available for free reading online.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://ebookjunkie.com/romance?page=1" target="_blank">eBook Junkie</a></strong>  23 free original works by generally unpublished authors available for free download in PDF.  A mix of short stories and novels.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.ebooknook.com/Free-Love-Story/love-story-catalogue.html" target="_blank"><u><strong>eBookNook (Romance)</strong></u></a> Around a hundred love stories available for reading online.</p>
