<p><strong><a href="http://www.ereaderiq.com/freebies" target="_blank">eReader IQ</a></strong>   due to the changes in Amazon policy, they now offer an "abbreviated" listing of the limited time free book offers from Amazon.  This link is to their Romance genre listing, with no adult content and has 19 free ebooks listed.   To show adult content, you have to click on the button on the upper right of the list.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://ereaderlove.com/" target="_blank">eReader Love</a></strong>    monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings.  This link is to their Romance genre listings and at the time of this post, there were 385 free ebooks listed.</p>
