<p><a href="http://rkphunt.com/index/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=section&amp;id=4&amp;Itemid=26" target="_blank"><strong>RKPHunt </strong></a>offers 5 full length novels for online reading.  One of the novels may be read without registering (free).  The other require registration.  There are also some other works available for reading after registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.roadtoromance.ca/freestories.htm" target="_blank">RoadtoRomance</a> </strong> has a listing of links to free romance novels for download in pdf or reading online.  Some are duplicates of this listing, but others are links to author sites. </p>
<p><a href="http://romanceatheart.com/fos.html" target="_blank"><strong>RomanceatHeart</strong></a> the online romance magazine has links to free online romance novels and short stories.  There are some unique entries here.  The links vary as to reading online or download in different formats.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.free-ebook-online.com/" target="_blank"><strong>RomanceCorner</strong></a> offers quite a few short works for online reading.  They look to be adult oriented works.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.romancenovel.tv/2009/05/20/free-reads/" target="_blank"><strong>RomanceNovelTV</strong></a> lists 7 romance novels available for free Kindle download at Amazon.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.romantic4ever.com/index.html" target="_blank"><strong>Romantic4Eve</strong>r</a> offers 2 free ebooks by author, Joan Reeves, as well as some short story romance fiction for reading online.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.romanticmarriagestories.com/" target="_blank"><strong>RomanticMarriageStories</strong></a>  features romance works about married life.  These short stories present a high view of marriage and portray the fun a romantic couple can have in a happy and sexy marriage.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.angelfire.com/mi2/mothersmemories/romance.html" target="_blank"><strong>Rosie'RomanticWritings </strong></a>offers the romantic novel, Forever More, for free reading online.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.reinkefreereads.blogspot.com/index.html" target="_blank">Sarah Reinke</a> </strong><strong> </strong>has made several of her romance novels, and some non-romance novels, available for download in pdf.  These are for mature audiences and you must be over 18 years of age to download.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://savannahchase.com/free-reads/" target="_blank">Savannah Chase</a></strong>  has made a good number of her short stories, flash fiction, novellas and poetry available for free.  Most are for free reading online and a few for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.shelleymunro.com/free-reads/" target="_blank">Shelley Munro</a></strong>  offers 6 of her novellas for free download in PDF.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.short-fiction.co.uk/newstories/categories.php" target="_blank">Short Fiction</a></strong> is a site for free short stories.  There are over 6,000 short stories in the various Romance and Erotic categories (over 18).  All are available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.shortstoriesfree.com/love-stories/love-stories.html" target="_blank">Short Stories Free</a></strong> offers 6 free short stories in its Love Stories collection.  All are available for free reading online, without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.short-fiction.co.uk/newstories/category_stories.php?category_id=5" target="_blank">Short Story Fiction (UK)</a></strong> has a 933  free short stories in their Romance genre available for free reading online without registration.  Also, <a href="http://www.short-fiction.co.uk/newstories/category_stories.php?category_id=28" target="_blank">Erotic Poetry</a>, <a href="http://www.short-fiction.co.uk/newstories/category_stories.php?category_id=26" target="_blank">Erotic Romance</a> and <a href="http://www.short-fiction.co.uk/newstories/category_stories.php?category_id=18" target="_blank">Erotic stories</a>.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.smashwords.com/books/category/876/newest/0/free/any" target="_blank"><strong>Smashwords</strong></a> has a large listing of free romance novels available for online reading or download in just about every reading format.  These are original and unpublished works.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://snickslist.com/books/browse-categories/" target="_blank">Snick's List</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />monitors Amazon (USA) for limited time free ebook offerings.  Nice category selection available. You will have to select Romance from the pull down category menu as they do not allow direct links to the category page.  eMail updates available.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://ebookstore.sony.com/search?&amp;page=1&amp;filters=4294967065+74" target="_blank">SonyReaderStore</a></strong> has 813 free romance novels available for free download through their free <strong><a href="http://ebookstore.sony.com/download/" target="_blank">Reader</a></strong> software.  I did not look through all the listings, but all of the novels appear to be from Smashwords (above).  You also do have to register, which is free and no billing information (credit card etc) is necessary.  I installed the software and registered and have received no spam.</p>
<p><b><a href="http://storybird.com/categories/romance/" target="_blank">Storybird</a></b>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />unites artists and writers to create some excellent illustrated stories.  On the left hand side of the page are the age divisions for the story's readers, ranging from preschool to adult. They claim there is over 5 million stories created there. Every story I saw was available for free reading and viewing online.  This link is to the Romance category.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://surrenderingpagesofromance.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Surrendering Pages of Romance</a></strong>   offers the free novel, <em>Surrendering,  </em>which is the first of 3 novels in the <em>Whispers of Desire</em> series.  Look on the right hand side of the page for links to the novel.  Available for free reading online without registration.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.bookdepository.com/dealsAndOffers/promo/id/100?searchSortBy=bestsellers&amp;promo=100&amp;searchTerm=&amp;category=2630" target="_blank">The Book Depository</a></strong> has 456 free ebooks in its Romance category available for free download in PDF without registration.  You will see prices listed for each of the books, but that is for hard copy.  Look for the green <em>Get Free eBook</em> to click on and then the green <em>Download Free eBook PDF</em> on the book listing page.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://the-cheap.net/category/genre/romance/" target="_blank">The Cheap</a></strong> is a site that monitors Amazon for limited time free offerings, which are generally recent releases.  Amazon does require registration and credit card info to download the free ebooks.  May also be limited by country.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.drabblecast.org/category/romance/" target="_blank">The Drabblecast</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />this is primarily a site for audio stories, but each story is also available for free reading online without registration.  This link is to the Romance category and there are over 30 free short stories.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.literaturepage.com/category/romance.html" target="_blank"><strong>TheLiteraturePage </strong></a>has 23 classic romance novels, plays and poems available for online viewing.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://onlinebooks.library.upenn.edu/webbin/book/browse?type=lcsubc&amp;key=Love%20stories" target="_blank">The Online Books Page</a></strong>  <img alt="" height="12" src="files/images/pc_freeware/free_online_books/srk-new.jpg" width="31" />maintains a collection of links to free Love Stories, both classic  and other public domain novels.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.trinitymoon.com/Articles-Book-Catalog.html" target="_blank"><strong>TrinityMoon</strong></a> a small collection of novels and short stories for online reading.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.wattpad.com/stories/romance" target="_blank"><strong>WattPad</strong></a> has over 500,000 free romance works available for free online reading.  These are original and unpublished works.  There mostly are short stories, but a good number of novels and novellas.  Nicely divided into sub-categories.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.web-books.com/Category.php?Category=Romance" target="_blank">Web-Books</a></strong> has 135 romance novels for free reading online or free download in WEBZ (reader information <a href="http://www.web-books.com/Web/WebBooks.htm" target="_blank"><strong>here</strong></a>).  these are classic works, but there are some unique entries here.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Category:Romance" target="_blank">WikiSource</a></strong>  has 13 classic romance novels available for free reading online.  There are also some free short stories available.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.thewildrosepress.com/free-reads-c-180.html" target="_blank"><strong>WildRosePress</strong></a> offers 73 short stories download in pdf or lit or reading online.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.worldwideschool.org/library/catalogs/bysubject-lit-romance.html" target="_blank"><strong>WorldWideSchoolLibrary</strong></a> has a nice collection of classic romance works available for free online reading.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.worthyofpublishing.com/top_lists.asp?genre=Romance" target="_blank"><strong>WorthyOfPublishing </strong></a>offers 2041 free romance novels for reading online.  These are original works by unpublished authors.</p>
